{
  "stem": "4760.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started to get basic religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But actually, the-- we had a beautiful temple in Laufersweiler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very conservative because the men were downstairs and the ladies were-- were upstairs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but we had no rabbi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The old-- the elderly men would conduct always the services.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They all were very well educated in-- in reading the Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have told us the Torah and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I grew up in Laufersweiler, it was difficult to go to school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in 1933, '34, the Hitler came to power, and the children hated all the Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for-- also the teachers, they hated the Jewish kids because the Jewish kids would raise their hand in school when-- to answer the questions of the teacher, and the teacher would say, why do-- does the Jewish kids always have to answer the questions and not you kids?",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would put us down all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to express ourself in school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But before that, before Hitler came into power--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only went to school in 1930, so there are only two years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we didn't see any difference between the children being mingled, and we were all friends and-- and enjoyed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We played soccer, we-- and we played in the [GERMAN] that's a sport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But once Hitler came, we were denied all this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our family was religious, but not over religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we would observe the Shabbos, the Sabbath Friday night, and the Shabbos in service.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was sometimes even difficult for my mother to observe the Sabbos because of the business she was in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandparents were in France, in Vic-Sur-Seille.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On my mother's side.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my grandfather from my father's side lived with us in the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
